data.description: DON'T MISS OUT!! Price Reduced!  This condo has been completely remodeled with all updates!  Clean & Move in Ready!  This condo offers two large bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms.  Located in the highly desirable Highland Lakes!.  Quartz counters in kitchen/baths.  All new paint, window treatments.  Luxury wood laminate flooring throughout.  Partial finished basement offers another kitchen area as well as tons of storage!  Club house activities include pools, tennis courts, basketball courts and remember so close to beautiful downtown Northville.
